Show HN: Alternative Tab Manager for Firefox
text:
This is an addon.

I'm using it exclusively for tab management.

I removed the bar bar with css to rely only on this.

It has a bunch of convenient features that you might like.

So far I find it very pleasant to use.

https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/grasshopper-urls/
